                    1986    1987    1988   1989    1990    1991
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
Aerosol              100     100      80     35      15      11
Refrigeration        100     102     103    108     100     104
Foams                100     112     120    111      97      87
Solvents and         100     104     111    100      90      76
Miscellaneous
